e optimum\ntime, this model could enable remote site characterisation using a large\narchive of weather forecasts and could be used to optimise the performance of\nwide-field AO system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Sep 2018 09:30:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-24"}
