elta/100$, every graph of maximum degree $\\Delta$ and clique number at most\n$\\Delta-k$ can be efficiently colored with at most $\\Delta-\\varepsilon k$\ncolors, for some absolute constant $\\varepsilon >0$, with a randomized\nalgorithm running in $O(\\log n/\\log \\log n)$ rounds with high probability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Sep 2018 14:16:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2018 12:35:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 24 Jan 2019 09:08:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-25"}
