pecies, and cannot treat the acid, base, and salt as neutral\nspecies. This emphasizes the differences between electrodiffusion and classical\nFickian diffusion, even at electroneutral scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Sep 2018 14:58:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Sep 2018 14:58:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2019 01:14:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-10"}
